Content:
A member of the Midnight Rangers, capable of acquiring information from winds.
When faced with protecting the things she dears most, Yangyang will not hesitate to convert her gentleness into blades.

A member of the Ministry of Development, able to turn her passion into bullets.
She has unlimited enthusiasm, just like her ammunition.

A botanist from New Federation who dwells in Huanglong, capable of hearing the sounds of plants.
The Starflowers that bloom on the vines are like her courage shining like stars.

Resonator with unknown identity. Possesses the power to absorb any sounds.
Sets on the journey for the purpose of retrieving memories.

Hierarch Guard, a person as cold as ice within the snow.
In her eyes, everything in this world will eventually be distorted into monstrous forms, only few shall maintain a pure reality.

The Acting Chief Officer of the Ministry of Development. Inherited the Might of Xuanwu. 
Under the relaxed and sluggish appearance, lies her duties of safeguarding the whole of Tiancheng.

Resonator with unknown identity. Possesses the power to absorb any sounds.
Sets on the journey for the purpose of retrieving memories.

An archaeologist of the Huanglong Academy, symbiotically connected with the Remnant called "You'tan".
Insists on the extreme rational principle of "Only Takes Responsibility for Herself", and often embarks on exploration of ruins on her own.

A member of the Black Shores Union emitting purity and cuteness, always seen accompanied by two Woolies, Cosmos and Cloudy.
An'ke's cheerfulness brings everyone joy, yet very few know of her fears when faced with darkness.

Member of the Midnight Rangers, with strong desires for affection for family.
If someone dares to harm her "family", she will give her all in order to safe keep it.

Leader of the Black Shores Union. Erratic and unpredictable like mist.
Hidden under his "play with life" attitude are always carefully thought-through plans.

Midnight Rangers' commander, Jiyan, is a man of righteous and resolute heart. He is able to bend the slightest breeze into the sharpest lance.
For the greater good of mankind, he is willing to challenge the destiny with his one man army.

Tacetite Specialist from New Federation who dwells in Huanglong. He turns his rage into power.
Lingering fury seems to burn behind his deep ruby eyes.

Huanglongese inquisitor. Pulls puppets with the power of thunder. Judges the weak ones lost in power.
Despite a member of Midnight Rangers, acts in a rogue way out of aloof personality

Boss at the Nightingale Tea House. Master of Tea Therapy and Bright Lightning Boxing.
Inside his fist aggression, indistinct lightning and delicate shows of plants are sensible.
